  "title": "6723 - External Audit Manager/ Audit Assistant Manager [Bugis]",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>5 days, 0830am - 1730pm</li>\n  <li>$4800 - $6500</li>\n  <li>Beach Road (Bugis)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manages a portfolio of engagements which includes client acceptance, engagement planning, execution and finalization of an audit engagement.</li>\n  <li>Fully accountable for the audit engagement and ensures that the engagement progress against budget and timeline is closely monitored.</li>\n  <li>Serves to develop and maintain long-term client relationships and value-add to the audit firm by identifying new business development opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Review and provides key technical expertise to ensure the quality of audit work performed is in compliance with professional standards and requirements.</li>\n  <li>Contributes towards continuous improvement in audit methodology and process.</li>\n  <li>Assume a greater role in professional development activities such as training, staff recruitment and resource planning.</li>\n  <li>required to plan, co-ordinate and supervisor various audit assignments for review by the engagement manager or partner.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's Degree or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 4 years of working experiences as Audit Assistant Manager or Audit Manager.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>https://wa.me/6596420989</strong></p>\n<p><strong>WhatsApp: +65 9642 0989 (Han)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Email: supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Chaw Chiaw Han, Reg No：R22106723</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd, EA No：14c7279</strong></p>",
